            "function": "Generate actions/narrative elements: Describe galloping, sunset, changing landscape (fields to woods/hills), 叶凌霜 observing surroundings, recalling fight details, thinking about 陆路通 (briefly, as per 表格3 note, maintaining hate), considering tactics for恶狼寨, feeling the night chill.",
            "input_data": ["Core Objective Function", "Deep Assessment Report"],
            "output_data": ["Set of Potential Actions/Narrative Elements (Journey Details, Environmental Shifts, Internal Monologue Threads)"]
          },
