            "primary_agent": "Hermes",
            "function": "Draft detailed descriptions of the scenery changing (colors, light, sounds), 叶凌霜's posture on horseback, her observations, her internal thoughts (tactics, memory flashes - carefully handled). Focus on sensory details to enrich the text and meet the word count. Ensure thoughts about 陆路通 are brief, emphasizing the 'hate' aspect and its paradoxical connection to her current state, as per 表格3 note 7 & 8.",
            "input_data": ["Selected Action Path", "Preliminary Narrative Concept", "Simulation Details"],
            "output_data": ["Detailed Interaction Design Draft (Rich descriptions, layered internal monologue)"]
