            "component_name": "Multidimensional Risk Assessor",
            "primary_agents": ["Apollo", "Ebing"],
            "function": "Assess risks: Primary risk is insufficient word count or repetitive descriptions. Minor risk of mishandling the 陆路通 memory flash (ensure it doesn't soften her resolve inappropriately). Check for logical consistency (travel time vs. distance - keep vague enough).",
