            "component_name": "Risk Mitigation & Design Refinement",
            "primary_agent": "Hermes",
            "consulting_agents": ["Apollo", "Ebing"],
            "function": "Mitigate risks: Add more varied sensory details (smell of dust/grass/pine, feel of wind, sounds of horse/night creatures). Ensure internal monologue varies between mission focus, past fight analysis, and brief, controlled flashes of memory. Explicitly manage the 陆路通 thought to reinforce the 'hate' motivation. Double-check word count during drafting.",
